    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Say goodbye to stubborn stains and dingy laundry with Soilove, the trusted solution for deep, residue-free cleaning. This powerful, unscented formula is designed to tackle the toughest soil and grime - from grass and grease to food and everyday messes - without compromising your clothes.</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Soilove Laundry Soil Stain Remover All Colorfast Washable Fabrics (Many Sizes)</h2>\n  <p>Say goodbye to stubborn stains and dingy laundry with Soilove, the trusted solution for deep, residue-free cleaning. This powerful, unscented formula is designed to tackle the toughest soil and grime - from grass and grease to food and everyday messes - without compromising your clothes.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>POWERFUL STAIN REMOVER - Effectively tackles tough stains like grease, dirt, grass, and food.</li>\n    <li>SAFE FOR ALL COLORFAST FABRICS - Cleans without fading or damaging your washable clothes.</li>\n    <li>RESIDUE-FREE FORMULA - Rinses clean with no buildup, film, or lingering chemicals.</li>\n    <li>UNSCENTED AND GENTLE - Ideal for sensitive skin and fragrance-free households.</li>\n    <li><strong>MADE IN THE USA - Quality you can trust, proudly produced domestically in a convenient bottle; 3 sizes available:</strong> 16oz, 22oz and 1 gallon</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/72265/nX7oHdBGR15O8tAc9ghCogxGWT5i7f-metac29pbG92ZV9wYXJlbnRfdXBkYXRlZC5qcGc=-.jpg\" alt=\"Say goodbye to stubborn stains and dingy laundry with Soilove, the trusted solution for deep, residue-free cleaning\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> SL60945PARENT</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> Green</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>Safe for all colorfast washable fabrics, Soilove lifts stains while preserving color and fabric integrity. It’s made in the USA and leaves no residue, just fresh, stain-free results you can see.</p>\n  <p>Whether you&#039;re refreshing workwear, sports uniforms, or everyday outfits, this bottle delivers big on performance in every wash.</p>\n  <p>3 Sizes Available: 16oz, 22oz and 1 Gallon (128oz)</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
